{"title":"2019-09-26","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>立山山域の大日岳へ。室堂付近はいつも通り中国人がいっぱい。室堂付近の紅葉は、あと一週間ほどで見頃かなぁ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-09-26/20190926-115314-P_20190926_115314.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-09-26/20190926-115314-P_20190926_115314.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>中華はうまい。しかし、うまい和食系は出先でなかなか見つからない。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2019/2019-09-28/20190926-183053-P_20190926_183053_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-09-28/20190926-183053-P_20190926_183053_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2019/2019-09-28/20190926-183547-P_20190926_183547.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2019/2019-09-28/20190926-183547-P_20190926_183547.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2019-09-29T02:12:46","published":"2019-09-29T02:12:46"}